high_descs: Turn left the walk straight, turn left facing the end of the table
Pick up the fork beside the tomato on the table
Turn right then go to the other side of the table on your left
Put the fork in the mug
Pick up the mug with fork
Turn right then head to the counter
Put the mug with fork on the counter beside the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with fork on the counter

high_descs: Make a left to walk around the green and white table, facing it.
Pick up the fork next to the red apple.
Walk around the table to reach the black cup sitting on the table.
Put the fork in the black cup.
Pick up the black cup with the fork in it.
Turn to face the countertop to the right of the sink.
Place the black cup with the fork to the right of the salt shaker on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Put a fork in a black cup to place next to the salt shaker on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the wall past the table, turn around, move to face the fork on the end of the table.
Pick up the fork on the table.
Bring the fork to the right side of the table, turn left to face the mug on the table.
Put the fork in the mug on the table.
Pick up the mug with fork on the table.
Bring the mug with fork to the counter behind you, right of the sink.
Put the mug with fork on the counter, left of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with fork on the counter, left of the coffee machine.
